<F P=102>  LD1001182394 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 1745 GMT 10 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1001182394 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Belgrade, 10 Jan (TANJUG) -- A session of the 
Supreme Defense Council was held in Belgrade today. It was 
presided over by the president of the Federal Republic of 
Yugoslavia. In addition to the members of the Supreme Defense 
Council -- Serbian President Slobodan Milosevic and Montenegrin 
President Momir Bulatovic -- the session was also attended by 
