<H3> <TI>   President Clinton To Visit in July </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1201113494 Warsaw PAP in Polish 1108 GMT 12 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1201113494 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw PAP </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Polish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Prague, 12 Jan -- Bill Clinton will pay a visit to 
Poland in July. During a meeting today, President Lech Walesa 
invited the U.S. President and, as PAP journalists heard from 
well-informed sources, the invitation has been accepted. The 
visit will probably take place in July during a European trip by 
the U.S. President, who will take part in a meeting of the 
leaders of the G7 nations. 

</TEXT>

