<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Bulgarian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Bulgarian delegation led by Finance Minister 
Stoyan Aleksandrov and the creditor banks of the so-called 
London Club, represented by Deutsche Bank, have just ended their 
two days of talks in Frankfurt. Here is our colleague 
Aleksandur Andreev of Deutsche Welle with a brief report on the 
talks supplied by Deutsche Bank. 
