and repayment of the Bulgarian foreign debt. The contracting 
parties also reached agreement on the time schedule for finally 
completing the documentation and concluding the negotiations on 
the restructuring of the Bulgarian foreign debt, which is 
expected to be completed before the end of June next year. [end 
recording] 

